title: Dickies Men's Light Compression Comfort Over-The-Calf Socks, Available in M-XXL (2, 4 Pairs)
description: Graduated 8-15 mmhg Compression Throughout Leg Improves Circulation to Reduce Leg Fatigue
Moisture Control Fibers Keeps Feet Dry. Content May Vary by Color
Light Weight Cushioned Leg and Full Cushioned Foot Bed

Comfortable over-the-calf Length to Improve Circulation Through the Calf Fighting Fatigue

Dickies light weight comfort compression socks for men circulation is engineered with gentle mild compression throughout the leg to improve circulation and fight leg fatigue. Compression socks are not too tight or hard to get it on and fit well, these socks are mild compression grade between 8~15mmHg.

Over the calf compression socks constructed with moisture control fibers, compression sock help improve performance, fast recovery, increase blood circulation and reduce fatigue. Perfect for long flight travel, long hour shifts, teachers, and seniors.

For Over 95 Years Dickies has been making hard-duty work products built to stand up to whatever life throws at you. Dickies Work Socks are built with purpose to deliver superior comfort and performance on and off the job.
